Package: hi-res-exporter
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: sklochkov2 <sklochkov2@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: systemd
Description: High-resolution Linux load Prometheus exporter
 A Prometheus exporter that samples Linux load signals at high frequency
 and exports percentiles over short rolling windows, making brief load
 bursts visible to dashboards and alerts.
